file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Named enums
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /v1/roles:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    OrderStatus:
      type: string
      enum: [Placed, Approved, Delivered]
    StatusCode:
      enum: [200, 400]
      x-enumNames: [Ok, BadRequest]
    ValidIdentifier:
      enum: [$, _, a1, 'привет', '日本', 'null', delete]
    InvalidIdentifier:
      enum: ['1', ' untrimmed ', '#', null, true, [1, 2]]
    RubiksCubeAlgorithm:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        additionalProperties: false
        properties:
          face:
            enum: [F, R, U, L, B, D]
          turns:
            enum: [-1, 1, 2]
        required:
          - face
          - turns
